text: Ani tyancyaca eka gatane pukaruna mhatale, he yasaribacya lokano! Tumacya thambanyace he sthana nahi, parata nigha ani tyanca eka dusara gata, paigambarajavala hi anumati magu lagala ki amaci ghare khali (ughadi) ani asuraksita aheta. Vastavika ti (ughadi) asuraksita navhati, (parantu) tyanni pala kadhanyaca pakka irada kela hota
